  <acronym>RM-SLM</acronym>
  <official_title>Rectal Misoprostol Versus Sublingual Misoprostol in Decreasing Blood Loss Prior to Abdominal Myomectomy: A Randomized Double-blinded Clinical Trial</official_title>
