  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the aim of the study is To compare the effectiveness of rectally administered prostaglandin
      E1 synthetic analogue (misoprostol) 400 microgram versus sublingually administered
      misoprostol before myomectomy to decrease blood loss during and after the operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
